trans-unit.source: Contains all of the data that is cached in the data island of a document-level customization.
trans-unit.target: 包含缓存在文档级自定义的数据岛中的所有数据。

trans-unit.source: For more information about caching data in document-level customizations, see [Caching Data](/visualstudio/vsto/caching-data.md) and [Accessing Data in Documents on the Server](/visualstudio/vsto/accessing-data-in-documents-on-the-server.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关在文档级自定义项中缓存数据的详细信息，请参阅[缓存数据](/visualstudio/vsto/caching-data.md)和[访问的服务器上的文档数据](/visualstudio/vsto/accessing-data-in-documents-on-the-server.md)。

trans-unit.source: Removes the cached data from the document of an Office solution and removes the description of the cached data from the cached data manifest.
trans-unit.target: 从 Office 解决方案的文档中删除缓存数据，并从缓存数据清单中删除缓存数据的说明。

trans-unit.source: To remove only the cached data and leave the description of the cached data in the cached data manifest, use the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedData.ClearData%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要删除缓存的数据，并在缓存的数据清单中留下的缓存的数据的说明，请使用<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedData.ClearData%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The cached data manifest is an XML description of the cached data in a document of an Office solution.
trans-unit.target: 缓存的数据清单文件为 Office 解决方案的文档中缓存的数据的 XML 说明。

trans-unit.source: Removes the cached data from the document of an Office solution.
trans-unit.target: 从 Office 解决方案的文档中删除缓存数据。

trans-unit.source: This method removes the cached data from the document of an Office solution, but does not remove the description of the cached data from the cached data manifest.
trans-unit.target: 此方法从 Office 解决方案的文档中删除缓存的数据，但不会从缓存的数据清单中删除缓存的数据的说明。

trans-unit.source: To remove the description of the cached data in the cached data manifest in addition to the cached data, use the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedData.Clear%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 若要在除了缓存的数据缓存的数据清单中删除缓存的数据的说明，使用<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedData.Clear%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The cached data manifest is an XML description of the cached data in a document of an Office solution.
trans-unit.target: 缓存的数据清单文件为 Office 解决方案的文档中缓存的数据的 XML 说明。

trans-unit.source: The XML string to use to reconstruct the cached data in the Office solution.
trans-unit.target: 用于重新构造 Office 解决方案中的缓存数据的 XML 字符串。

trans-unit.source: Reconstructs the cached data in the Office solution from an XML string.
trans-unit.target: 在 Office 解决方案中从 XML 字符串重新构造缓存数据。

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="cachedDataManifest" /> is <see langword="null" /> or an empty string.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="cachedDataManifest" /> 为 <see langword="null" /> 或空字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItem" /> objects that are in the data cache.
trans-unit.target: 获取数据缓存中 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItem" /> 对象的集合。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItemCollection" /> that contains the data in the data cache.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.Tools.Applications.CachedDataHostItemCollection" /> ，其中包含数据缓存中的数据。

trans-unit.source: Returns the serialized XML representation of the data that is cached in a document of an Office solution.
trans-unit.target: 返回在 Office 解决方案的文档中缓存的数据的序列化 XML 表示形式。

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the serialized XML representation of the data that is cached in a document of an Office solution.
trans-unit.target: 包含在 Office 解决方案的文档中缓存的数据的序列化 XML 表示形式的字符串。
